Effective Date: 04-07-2024

1. Introduction

Welcome to Connectify! This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our bot on Discord. Please read this policy carefully to understand our views and practices regarding your personal data and how we will treat it.

2. Information We Collect

We collect the following types of information:

a. Personal Information:

Discord Username: To identify you and personalize your experience.
Profile Information: Interests, needs, and any other information you provide in your profile.

b. Usage Data:

Commands Usage: Information about the commands you use and your interactions with Connectify.

3. How We Use Your Information

We use the information we collect in the following ways:

To operate and maintain the Connectify bot.
To match users with similar interests and needs.
To facilitate real-time chatting and community building.
To improve and customize our services based on user feedback and usage patterns.

4. Information Sharing and Disclosure

We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to outside parties except in the following circumstances:

With your explicit consent.
To comply with legal obligations or protect our rights and the rights of other users.
To trusted third-party service providers who assist us in operating our bot and conducting our business, provided those parties agree to keep this information confidential.
5. Data Security

We implement a variety of security measures to maintain the safety of your personal information. However, no method of transmission over the Internet or electronic storage is 100% secure. Therefore, we cannot guarantee absolute security.

6. Your Data Protection Rights

Depending on your location, you may have the following rights regarding your personal data:

The right to access – You have the right to request copies of your personal data.
The right to rectification – You have the right to request that we correct any information you believe is inaccurate or complete information you believe is incomplete.
The right to erasure – You have the right to request that we erase your personal data, under certain conditions.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at our discord server.

